Package org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.ieee1609dot2.generator.receiver

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Receiver
    Generic interface for a receiver used during decryption.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasePKReceiver
    Base class containing common methods for all Public Key Receivers.
    CertificateReciever
    Receiver using a certificate to envelope decryption key.
    PreSharedKeyReceiver
    Receiver using a pre-shared key.
    RekReciever
    PublicKey Receiver used for public keys not associated with any certificate or SignedData.
    SignedDataReciever
    Receiver using public key based on signed data structure.
    SymmetricKeyReceiver
    Receiver when enveloping the symmetric encryption key with another symmetric key.
